<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.8.4">
<l>celakkāṇ kiṟpār kāṇu maḷavuñ celluṅ kīrttiyā</l>
<l>yulappi lāṉē yellā vulaku muṭaiya vorumūrtti</l>
<l>nalattāṉ mikkār kuṭantaik kiṭantā yuṉṉaik kāṇpāṉnā</l>
<l>ṉalappāyākā cattai nōkki yaḻuvaṉ ṟoḻuvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You of a fame that goes beyond the measure that is seen by those who can see [it] go,</l>
<l>one without death, [your] one form possesses all the worlds.</l>
<l>You who lie in Kuṭantai very full of goodness, in order to see you I,</l>
<l>in confusion looking at the firmanent, I cry, I worship.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
